metadata.name: Jane Doe
metadata.description:
100% of the proceeds from this sale will go directly to Fund Texas Choice, an organization that provides travel assistance and accommodations for Texas residents to access safe abortions, whether their appointments are located in Texas or out-of-state. They also help connect those in need with organizations that provide funding for the procedure itself. 

Thank you for helping support this incredibly important cause, and fighting for a safe and fair future for all. 

For more information, go to https://fundtexaschoice.org/. For more places to donate, check out https://www.thecut.com/article/donate-abortion-fund-roe-v-wade-how-to-help.html
